descr: "The MeasureReport resource contains the results of evaluating a measure."

fields.name: identifier
fields.descr: "The identifier of this stratifier, as defined in the measure definition."

fields.name: stratum
fields.descr: "This element contains the results for a single stratum within the stratifier. For example, when stratifying on administrative gender, there will be four strata, one for each possible gender value."
